dict.string: Omny requires access to the camera to allow users to scan the qr code and make video calls and communicate in real time with other users. For example, you might use your camera to join a video call with a friend

To improve your experience and ensure security, Omny requires access to your location to determine if you’re close to your home, For example, when you unzip the qr code in the app, we could use GPS to track your location and allow you to make the video call
